### ============================================
### 3. TRAMOS - CREACIÓN
### ============================================

### 3.1 Crear nuevo tramo (mínimo requerido)
# @name createMinimal
POST {{baseUrl}}/tramos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ILO-CBA",
  "name": "Ilo - Cochabamba",
  "origin": "Ilo",
  "destination": "Cochabamba"
}

